I can't support this proposal, mainly because I think such a fine-grained 
topic-based partition of the list is unlikely to be widely understood or 
observed.

As a solution to the volume problem, I've found it convenient to follow this 
list via the Gmane RSS feed (http://rss.gmane.org/gmane.comp.lang.caml.inria). 
Tabbing through posts in a feed reader is much less hassle then deleting emails 
from your inbox.

